2) In src, go into Makefile.conf.AIX, you'll see this:

INCcrtm = /emc2/wx20er/nextjif/nam_wrf/sorc/nam_gsi.fd/include_crtm2
LIBcrtm = /emc2/wx20er/nextjif/nam_wrf/sorc/nam_gsi.fd/libcrtm2/libcrtm.a
##INCcrtm = /nwprod/sorc/nam_gsi.fd/include_crtm2
##LIBcrtm = /nwprod/sorc/nam_gsi.fd/libcrtm2/libcrtm.a
                                                                                                                                     
WRFPATH=/emc2/wx20er/nextjif/nam_wrf/sorc/nam_nmm_real_fcst.fd
#WRFPATH=/nwprod/sorc/nam_nmm_real_fcst.fd

As with the other codes, comment out the /emc2 paths and uncomment the /nwprod paths; make sure the WRF-NMM model code is compiled first

3) type "./configure"

4) type "make" which will start compiling the code

